oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Marquis L. Fowlkes' house
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Photograph of Marquis L. Fowlkes' house located in Bakerville. Four people are posed in front of the house next to a horse-drawn buggy. Two of the people shown are Capt. W. W. Hobbs and Victoria Fowlkes Hobbs.
